      "html": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n  <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n  <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n  <title>AI Lawyer - AI-Powered Legal Assistant for Startups</title>\n  <meta name=\"description\" content=\"Get expert legal help for your startup with AI-powered contract review, compliance monitoring, and document analysis.\">\n  <link rel=\"preconnect\" href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com\">\n  <link href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n  <style>\n    :root {\n      --primary: #1a1a2e;\n      --secondary: #16213e;\n      --accent: #0f3460;\n      --font: 'Inter', sans-serif;\n      --radius: 8px;\n    }\n    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }\n    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }\n    body { font-family: var(--font); line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }\n    .container { max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 24px; }\n\n    /* Header */\n    header { padding: 16px 0; background: var(--primary); color: white; position: sticky; top: 0; z-index: 100; }\n    header nav { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; }\n    .logo { font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 700; }\n    .logo span { color: #e94560; }\n    .nav-links { display: flex; gap: 32px; list-style: none; }\n    .nav-links a { color: white; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 500; transition: opacity 0.2s; }\n    .nav-links a:hover { opacity: 0.8; }\n    .nav-cta { background: #e94560; padding: 10px 24px; border-radius: var(--radius); color: white; font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none; transition: transform 0.2s; }\n    .nav-cta:hover { transform: translateY(-1px); }\n\n    /* Hero */\n    .hero { padding: 100px 0; text-align: center; background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary) 0%, var(--secondary) 50%, var(--accent) 100%); color: white; position: relative; overflow: hidden; }\n    .hero::before { content: ''; position: absolute; top: -50%; left: -50%; width: 200%; height: 200%; background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(233,69,96,0.1) 0%, transparent 50%); animation: pulse 8s ease-in-out infinite; }\n    @keyframes pulse { 0%, 100% { transform: scale(1); } 50% { transform: scale(1.1); } }\n    .hero h1 { font-size: 3.5rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 24px; position: relative; }\n    .hero h1 span { color: #e94560; }\n    .hero p { font-size: 1.25rem; max-width: 650px; margin: 0 auto 40px; opacity: 0.9; position: relative; }\n    .hero-cta { display: inline-flex; gap: 16px; position: relative; }\n    .btn-primary { padding: 16px 36px; background: #e94560; color: white; border: none; border-radius: var(--radius); font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 600; cursor: pointer; transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s; text-decoration: none; }\n    .btn-primary:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(233,69,96,0.4); }\n    .btn-secondary { padding: 16px 36px; background: transparent; color: white; border: 2px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.3); border-radius: var(--radius); font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 600; cursor: pointer; transition: border-color 0.2s; text-decoration: none; }\n    .btn-secondary:hover { border-color: white; }\n\n    /* Features */\n    .features { padding: 100px 0; background: #f8f9fa; }\n    .features h2 { text-align: center; font-size: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 16px; color: var(--primary); }\n    .features .subtitle { text-align: center; font-size: 1.1rem; color: #666; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto 64px; }\n    .features-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(320px, 1fr)); gap: 32px; }\n    .feature-card { padding: 40px 32px; background: white; border-radius: var(--radius); border: 1px solid #eee; transition: transform 0.3s, box-shadow 0.3s; }\n    .feature-card:hover { transform: translateY(-4px); box-shadow: 0 12px 32px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); }\n    .feature-icon { width: 56px; height: 56px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary), var(--accent)); border-radius: 12px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 20px; color: white; }\n    .feature-card h3 { font-size: 1.25rem; margin-bottom: 12px; color: var(--primary); }\n    .feature-card p { color: #666; font-size: 0.95rem; }\n\n    /* Stats */\n    .stats { padding: 80px 0; background: var(--primary); color: white; }\n    .stats-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr)); gap: 32px; text-align: center; }\n    .stat h3 { font-size: 3rem; font-weight: 700; color: #e94560; margin-bottom: 8px; }\n    .stat p { font-size: 1rem; opacity: 0.8; }\n\n    /* CTA */\n    .cta-section { padding: 100px 0; text-align: center; }\n    .cta-section h2 { font-size: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 16px; color: var(--primary); }\n    .cta-section p { font-size: 1.1rem; color: #666; max-width: 500px; margin: 0 auto 40px; }\n\n    /* Footer */\n    footer { padding: 48px 0; background: var(--primary); color: white; }\n    .footer-content { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 24px; }\n    .footer-links { display: flex; gap: 24px; list-style: none; }\n    .footer-links a { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7); text-decoration: none; transition: color 0.2s; }\n    .footer-links a:hover { color: white; }\n\n    @media (max-width: 768px) {\n      .hero h1 { font-size: 2.2rem; }\n      .hero p { font-size: 1rem; }\n      .hero-cta { flex-direction: column; align-items: center; }\n      .features-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }\n      .nav-links { display: none; }\n      .footer-content { flex-direction: column; text-align: center; }\n    }\n  </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n  <header>\n    <div class=\"container\">\n      <nav>\n        <div class=\"logo\">AI <span>Lawyer</span></div>\n        <ul class=\"nav-links\">\n          <li><a href=\"#features\">Features</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"#stats\">Results</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"#cta\">Pricing</a></li>\n        </ul>\n        <a href=\"#cta\" class=\"nav-cta\">Get Started</a>\n      </nav>\n    </div>\n  </header>\n\n  <main>\n    <section class=\"hero\">\n      <div class=\"container\">\n        <h1>AI-Powered <span>Legal Assistant</span> for Startups</h1>\n        <p>Get expert legal help without the expert price tag. AI Lawyer provides automated contract review, compliance monitoring, and document analysis for startup founders.</p>\n        <div class=\"hero-cta\">\n          <a href=\"#cta\" class=\"btn-primary\">Start Free Trial</a>\n          <a href=\"#features\" class=\"btn-secondary\">See How It Works</a>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section class=\"features\" id=\"features\">\n      <div class=\"container\">\n        <h2>Powerful Legal AI at Your Fingertips</h2>\n        <p class=\"subtitle\">Everything your startup needs to stay legally compliant, powered by cutting-edge artificial intelligence.</p>\n        <div class=\"features-grid\">\n          <div class=\"feature-card\">\n            <div class=\"feature-icon\">📋</div>\n            <h3>Contract Review</h3>\n            <p>Upload any contract and receive instant analysis. Our AI identifies risky clauses, suggests improvements, and ensures your interests are protected.</p>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"feature-card\">\n            <div class=\"feature-icon\">🛡️</div>\n            <h3>Compliance Monitoring</h3>\n            <p>Stay compliant with ever-changing regulations. AI Lawyer monitors your documents and alerts you to potential compliance issues before they become problems.</p>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"feature-card\">\n            <div class=\"feature-icon\">📄</div>\n            <h3>Document Analysis</h3>\n            <p>Deep analysis of legal documents with plain-English summaries. Understand exactly what you're signing without expensive lawyer consultations.</p>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section class=\"stats\" id=\"stats\">\n      <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"stats-grid\">\n          <div class=\"stat\">\n            <h3>10,000+</h3>\n            <p>Contracts Reviewed</p>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"stat\">\n            <h3>95%</h3>\n            <p>Accuracy Rate</p>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"stat\">\n            <h3>$2M+</h3>\n            <p>Legal Fees Saved</p>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"stat\">\n            <h3>500+</h3>\n            <p>Happy Startups</p>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section class=\"cta-section\" id=\"cta\">\n      <div class=\"container\">\n        <h2>Ready to Protect Your Startup?</h2>\n        <p>Join hundreds of startup founders who trust AI Lawyer for their legal needs. Start your free trial today.</p>\n        <a href=\"#\" class=\"btn-primary\">Get Started Free</a>\n      </div>\n    </section>\n  </main>\n\n  <footer>\n    <div class=\"container\">\n      <div class=\"footer-content\">\n        <div class=\"logo\">AI <span>Lawyer</span></div>\n        <ul class=\"footer-links\">\n          <li><a href=\"#features\">Features</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"#stats\">Results</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"#cta\">Pricing</a></li>\n        </ul>\n        <p>&copy; 2026 AI Lawyer. All rights reserved.</p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </footer>\n</body>\n</html>"
